         <div type="translation" resp="part:vito">
             <p>Hommage to the Bhagavant, the Buddha! In the … year of King Māṭharīputta Siri-Puḷumāvi, … on the 5th day. A slab with a<supplied reason="subaudible">n engraved</supplied> shrine: the pious gift of Kaṇhasiri of the Hāga family, an <foreign>upāsaka</foreign> from Mount Siddhaka, the son of the merchant -deva—together with his mother, his brother<supplied reason="subaudible">s</supplied>, his son<supplied reason="subaudible">s</supplied>—for the well-being of the whole world.</p>
             <!--translation encoded as per EGD §9.2 -->
